---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Agenda una demo — SACS"
  description="Agenda una demo personalizada de 30 minutos con un experto de SACS. Te mostramos la plataforma funcionando con datos de tu negocio."
>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="demo-hero">
  <div class="demo-hero-inner">
    <div class="demo-hero-content">
      <span class="demo-eyebrow">Sin compromiso, sin tarjeta</span>
      <h1 class="demo-hero-title">Ve SACS en accion con datos de tu negocio</h1>
      <p class="demo-hero-subtitle">En 30 minutos te mostramos como gestionar ventas, inventario, clientes y lealtad en un solo lugar. Personalizado para tu tipo de negocio.</p>
      <div class="demo-hero-benefits">
        <div class="demo-benefit">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 2a8 8 0 100 16 8 8 0 000-16z" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M7 10l2 2 4-4" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          <span>Demo personalizada de 30 min</span>
        </div>
        <div class="demo-benefit">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 2a8 8 0 100 16 8 8 0 000-16z" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M7 10l2 2 4-4" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          <span>Con un experto en retail</span>
        </div>
        <div class="demo-benefit">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 2a8 8 0 100 16 8 8 0 000-16z" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M7 10l2 2 4-4" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          <span>Sin compromiso ni tarjeta de credito</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="demo-hero-calendly" id="demo">
      <div class="demo-calendly-card">
        <h2 class="demo-calendly-title">Elige tu horario</h2>
        <p class="demo-calendly-desc">Selecciona el dia y hora que mejor te funcione.</p>
        <div class="demo-calendly-embed" id="calendly-embed">
          <div class="demo-calendly-placeholder">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
            <p>Cargando calendario...</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Trust bar -->
<section class="demo-trust">
  <div class="demo-trust-inner">
    <div class="demo-trust-item">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-secondary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
      <div>
        <span class="demo-trust-num">3,000+</span>
        <span class="demo-trust-label">marcas activas</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="demo-trust-item">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M10 1l2.39 4.84L18 6.71l-4 3.9.94 5.5L10 13.48l-4.94 2.63.94-5.5-4-3.9 5.61-.87L10 1z" fill="#E8A838" transform="translate(2,2) scale(0.85)"/></svg>
      <div>
        <span class="demo-trust-num">4.8/5</span>
        <span class="demo-trust-label">Google Reviews</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="demo-trust-item">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-secondary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
      <div>
        <span class="demo-trust-num">99.9%</span>
        <span class="demo-trust-label">uptime garantizado</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="demo-trust-item">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-secondary)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
      <div>
        <span class="demo-trust-num">15 min</span>
        <span class="demo-trust-label">para configurar</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- What to expect -->
<section class="demo-section">
  <div class="demo-section-inner">
    <h2 class="demo-section-title">Que veras en la demo</h2>
    <p class="demo-section-desc">Te mostramos SACS funcionando con un escenario real de tu industria. No slides, no presentaciones genericas.</p>
    <div class="demo-steps">
      <div class="demo-step">
        <span class="demo-step-num">01</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Entendemos tu negocio</h3>
          <p>Nos cuentas como operas hoy, cuantas sucursales tienes, que canales usas y que te duele de tu operacion actual.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="demo-step">
        <span class="demo-step-num">02</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Demo personalizada</h3>
          <p>Te mostramos SACS funcionando con datos y escenarios de tu tipo de negocio: punto de venta, inventario, clientes, reportes y mas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="demo-step">
        <span class="demo-step-num">03</span>
        <div>
          <h3>Plan de implementacion</h3>
          <p>Definimos juntos los siguientes pasos, tiempos de migracion y como empezar. Sin presion, sin compromiso.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Testimonial -->
<section class="demo-section demo-section--alt">
  <div class="demo-section-inner">
    <blockquote class="demo-quote">
      <p>"En un concierto llegamos a perder el 20% de nuestras ventas en solo dos horas porque el sistema cayo. Con SACS eso no vuelve a pasar."</p>
      <cite>— Mariana Lopez, Directora de Operaciones, Liveshow Merchandising</cite>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Industries -->
<section class="demo-section">
  <div class="demo-section-inner">
    <h2 class="demo-section-title">SACS funciona para tu tipo de negocio</h2>
    <div class="demo-industries">
      <div class="demo-industry">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
        <span>Tiendas y boutiques</span>
      </div>
      <div class="demo-industry">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 00-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 00-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 003 8v8a2 2 0 001 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 002 0l7-4A2 2 0 0021 16z"/><path d="M3.27 6.96L12 12.01l8.73-5.05M12 22.08V12"/></svg>
        <span>Multi-sucursal</span>
      </div>
      <div class="demo-industry">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg>
        <span>E-commerce</span>
      </div>
      <div class="demo-industry">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 010 8h-1M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 01-4 4H6a4 4 0 01-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg>
        <span>Cafeterias y restaurantes</span>
      </div>
      <div class="demo-industry">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
        <span>Eventos y merchandising</span>
      </div>
      <div class="demo-industry">
        <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-primary)" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2a4 4 0 014 4v1a1 1 0 001 1h1a4 4 0 010 8h-1a1 1 0 00-1 1v1a4 4 0 01-8 0v-1a1 1 0 00-1-1H6a4 4 0 010-8h1a1 1 0 001-1V6a4 4 0 014-4z"/></svg>
        <span>Moda y lifestyle</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Final CTA -->
<section class="demo-final-cta">
  <div class="demo-final-inner">
    <h2>Tambien puedes escribirnos</h2>
    <p>Si prefieres chatear directamente, contactanos por WhatsApp.</p>
    <a id="demo-wa-link" href="https://wa.me/5215536634392" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="demo-wa-btn">
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
      Escribenos por WhatsApp
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ── Hero ── */
  .demo-hero {
    background: #0f0f1a;
    padding: clamp(80px, 8vw, 120px) 0 clamp(60px, 6vw, 80px);
  }
  .demo-hero-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(20px, 4vw, 48px);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr;
    gap: clamp(40px, 5vw, 80px);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .demo-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .demo-hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4.5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }
  .demo-hero-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.125rem);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    max-width: 480px;
  }
  .demo-hero-benefits {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .demo-benefit {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  }
  .demo-benefit svg { flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* ── Calendly Card ── */
  .demo-calendly-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }
  .demo-calendly-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }
  .demo-calendly-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 24px;
  }
  .demo-calendly-placeholder {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
    min-height: 400px;
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }
  .demo-calendly-placeholder p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Trust Bar ── */
  .demo-trust {
    background: #fff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }
  .demo-trust-inner {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 28px clamp(20px, 4vw, 48px);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .demo-trust-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .demo-trust-item svg { flex-shrink: 0; }
  .demo-trust-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    display: block;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .demo-trust-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    display: block;
  }

  /* ── Sections ── */
  .demo-section {
    padding: clamp(60px, 8vw, 100px) 24px;
    background: #fff;
  }
  .demo-section--alt {
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
  }
  .demo-section-inner {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .demo-section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .demo-section-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 40px;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  /* ── Steps ── */
  .demo-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 32px;
  }
  .demo-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .demo-step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .demo-step h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 6px;
  }
  .demo-step p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Quote ── */
  .demo-quote {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    padding-left: 28px;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 640px;
  }
  .demo-quote p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.5vw, 1.3rem);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }
  .demo-quote cite {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
  }

  /* ── Industries ── */
  .demo-industries {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
  .demo-industry {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }
  .demo-industry span {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  /* ── Final CTA ── */
  .demo-final-cta {
    padding: clamp(60px, 8vw, 100px) 24px;
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .demo-final-inner {
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .demo-final-cta h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }
  .demo-final-cta p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0 0 24px;
  }
  .demo-wa-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    background: #25D366;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .demo-wa-btn:hover {
    background: #20bd5a;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  /* ── Mobile ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .demo-hero-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .demo-hero-content {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .demo-hero-subtitle {
      margin-inline: auto;
    }
    .demo-hero-benefits {
      align-items: center;
    }
    .demo-trust-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .demo-industries {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  {
    // WhatsApp link with page context
    const waLink = document.getElementById('demo-wa-link') as HTMLAnchorElement;
    if (waLink) {
      const msg = encodeURIComponent('Hola, me interesa agendar una demo de SACS. Estaba viendo: ' + window.location.href);
      waLink.href = `https://wa.me/5215536634392?text=${msg}`;
    }

    // Scroll to demo section if #demo hash
    if (window.location.hash === '#demo') {
      const el = document.getElementById('demo');
      if (el) {
        setTimeout(() => el.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' }), 300);
      }
    }
  }
</script>
</BaseLayout>
